songs.title: Behind Enemy Lines (Live)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Demi Lovato]
(Laughs)
Alright, you guys ready?
Put your hands together!

[Verse 1: Demi Lovato]
And I feel
I feel a deep connection
And I think
That we might be onto something, no
And I know it's something special
Seeing you here is not coincidental, mhmm

[Chorus: Demi Lovato]
But I've been walking, walking behind enemy lines
And I've been fighting, fighting from the other side
I've been saying, saying I won't fall this time
But now I'm walking, walking within enemy lines
Mhmm, oh

[Verse 2: Demi Lovato]
See I was trying to be everything you weren't expecting
All I ever wanted was to try and keep you guessing
But I'm falling way too fast
I just want this love to last forever, forever
But every time I feel this way
Oh, somethings changed for the better
(Whoa whoa whoa oooh)

[Chorus: Demi Lovato]
So I was walking, walking behind enemy lines
And I've been fighting, fighting from the other side
I've been saying, saying that I won't fall this time
But now I'm walking, walking within enemy lines

[Chorus: Demi Lovato]
And I've been walking, walking behind enemy lines
And I've been fighting, fighting from the other side
I've been saying, saying I won't fall this time
But now I'm walking, walking within enemy lines
Uh uh uh uh
Ay ay ay ay ay ay ay

[Outro: Demi Lovato]
Thank you!
Thank you so much!
